org.sql: SELECT changesets.* FROM changesets INNER JOIN repositories ON repositories.id = changesets.repository_id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = repositories.project_id WHERE changesets.user_id = 3 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'repository') IS NOT NULL ORDER BY changesets.id DESC LIMIT 1
